OL,3,CMushroom company fined after worker
OL,4,Closes leg
OL,6,FA company that grows mushrooms has
OL,7,Fbeen ordered to pay more than #80,000
OL,8,Fafter a worker lost a leg following an
OL,9,Faccident.
OL,11,FLuka Ilic's right leg was caught in
OL,12,Fthe rotating blades of a mushroom
OL,13,Ffilling machine on 16 October 2019.
OL,15,FThe 29-year-old was part of a cleaning
OL,16,Fteam at Howden Enterprises Ltd,
OL,17,Ftrading under the name Hughes
OL,18,FMushrooms, in Holme-on-Spalding-Moor,
OL,19,FEast Yorkshire.
