OL,6,FThe machine was turned on after he
OL,7,Fclimbed onto it to remove compost,
OL,8,Fcausing his leg to becoming trapped.
OL,10,FIt was later amputated below the knee.
OL,12,FA Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,13,Finvestigation found Howden Enterprises
OL,14,Ffailed to adequately assess the
OL,15,Foperation of the machine, in
OL,16,Fparticular suring cleaning.
