OL,3,CMushroom company fined after worker
OL,4,Closes leg
OL,6,FInspector Louise Redgrove said: "The
OL,7,Fimportance of a suitable and
OL,8,Fsufficient risk assessment which
OL,9,Freflects all actual practical
OL,10,Factivities cannot be underestimated.
OL,12,F"It is vital to ensure there are
OL,13,Feffective systems of work and physical
OL,14,Fcontrols which are implemented,
OL,15,Fsupervised and used by all those
OL,16,Finvolved.
OL,18,F"This incident could have easily been
OL,19,Favoided with a robust isolation
OL,20,Fprocedure and padlock for each worker
OL,21,Finvolved."
